race.comment: MARGOT'S DEEL (16) goes well for hoop Graham who has two wins and two placings from just four steers and is racing very consistently this time in work. Only needs some luck from the wide draw to be right in the finish again. VORACIOUS (11) has only missed a drum once in five attempts over this mile journey and will be rock-hard fit for this. Likely to feature. EXPRESS PAYMENT (1) is a two-time winner over this course and distance and gets some weight relief with the 3kg claim. One for the exotics players. LOST HIS BEANS (3) best of the rest out of the Vandyke stable.
